obvious.impl
Class TupleImpl

java.lang.Object
  obvious.impl.TupleImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
Tuple
Direct Known Subclasses:
EdgeImpl, NodeImpl
public class TupleImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements Tuple

Example implementation of Tuple Interface. This class should be used when for an Obvious binding, the source implementation does not offer the notion of tuple.

Author:
Pierre-Luc Hemery
